#. Tag: title
#: using-d-i.xml:1885
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Installing Additional Software"
msgstr "安裝基本系統"

#. Tag: para
#: using-d-i.xml:1886
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After the base system is installed, you have a usable but limited system. "
